node.text: That’s a big ass flagstick! Best caption wins a new @cactushackgolf polo. With the cool technology in this fabric and the temps we play in Arizona in the summer without it sticking to your body from sweat I promise you you’ll never put on a better polo in your life.

node.text:
It took longer than normal to open this business but here we are. We both have been into health and fitness for a long time but Over the last year n half due to my injuries and interest into anti aging, recovery and overall health of the body we decided to open our own clinic. 
_
You can book online at thecurewellness.com or head to the App Store and download our app and book your mobile IV or head into the clinic at 2012 N Scottsdale RD right behind Dutch bros and next to rock church. Mention this post and get 30% off your first IV. Appreciate all the love and support as always.
